This paper deals with the efficient allocation of resources in cloud environments, which is a topic that falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper discusses Service Level Agreements (SLAs) and their manipulation, which is related to Networked Systems (cs.NI) and Systems and Control (cs.SY). The paper also presents simulation results, which could fall under the category of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) or Software Engineering (cs.SE) depending on the specific focus of the simulations.
